{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "pam-re-90d-001",
    "name": "SupplyChain-PAM-RevenueElasticity-90d",
    "description": "ACTUS PAM contract: REVENUE ELASTICITY (GTAP) single-factor simulation.\n\n$5M WC loan, IN-textiles corridor.\nArmington elasticity 2.8 → 49% revenue decline.\n\nPer ACTUS official documentation:\n- PAM: Principal At Maturity\n- See: https://documentation.actusfrf.org/docs/examples/basic-contract-types/example_PAM\n\nRisk Factor: REVENUE ELASTICITY (GTAP) model only (single dimension).\nBehavioral model from Risk-Factor-2.md Domain 2: Tariff/Trade Finance.",
